se></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 27, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ypk1719469595014.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ypk1719469595014.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ypk1719469595014.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xrv1665703127316\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Image\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"xrv1665703127316__image_386960\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This widget displays an image that can represent a hyperlink, have alternative text, or make use of other features that are not available in the picture control.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xrv1665703127316__topic_d115208e1_d115209e1_d115210e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xrv1665703127316__p_d115211e1_d115212e1_d115213e1\">XHTML Specification: <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;x-subst type=\"image\"&gt;</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xrv1665703127316__p_d115214e1_d115215e1_d115216e1\">For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fdp1719467376341.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fdp1719467376341.html\" title=\"XHTML placeholder for the USP widget and field data that will be generated in the HTML sent to the browser.\">&lt;x-subst type=\"WidgetType\"&gt;</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xrv1665703127316__topic_d81752e1_d81753e1_d81754e1_d81755e1_d81756e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d371695e72\">\n                       \n Widget Properties\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Widget Properties</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__1\">\n Property\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__2\">\n Description/More Information\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"npf1665703108397.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/npf1665703108397.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the path and file name of the image to display. This property sets the src attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout of the static server page.\">Image Source (u_src)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__2\">\n Path and file name of the image to display.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"twd1665703108686.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/twd1665703108686.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the target URL of a hyperlink or image in a static server page.\">Link Value (u_url)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__2\">\n Target URL for a link.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jqu1665703109428.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jqu1665703109428.html\" title=\"Widget property in a static server page that determines the window into which the linked page is loaded.\">Target Window (u_target)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__2\">\n Type of target window into which the linked page is loaded.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pqj1665703109065.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pqj1665703109065.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the path and file name of a low-resolution image to display in the server page while the main image is loading. It sets the lowsrc attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout.\">Shadow Image (u_lowsrc)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__2\">\n Path and file name of a low-resolution image to display in the server page while the main image is loading.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uha1665703107266.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uha1665703107266.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the text describing an image in a static server page. It sets the alt attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout.\">Alternative Text (u_alt)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__2\">\n Text that is displayed if the image cannot be loaded.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nfw1665703107564.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nfw1665703107564.html\" title=\"This widget property defines how an image is aligned within the field in a static server page. It sets the align attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout.\">Alignment (u_align)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__2\">\n Determines how the image is aligned in the field.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rks1665703107638.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rks1665703107638.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the width of a border, in pixels, that surrounds an image. This property sets the border attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout of the static server page.\">Border (u_border)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__2\">\n Width, in pixels, of the border that surrounds the image.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"efb1665703108245.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/efb1665703108245.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the number of pixels of white space to be inserted to the left and right of the image. This property sets the hspace attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout of the static server page.\">Horizontal Spaces (u_hspace)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__2\">\n Number of pixels of white space to be inserted to the left and right of the image.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"usg1665703109942.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/usg1665703109942.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the number of pixels of white space to be inserted above and below the image in a static server page. It sets the vspace attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout.\">Vertical Spaces (u_vspace)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__2\">\n Number of pixels of white space to be inserted above and below the image.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sba1665703110233.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sba1665703110233.html\" title=\"Widget property that defines the width of the displayed image in a static server page. It sets the width attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout.\">Width (u_width)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__2\">\n Width, in pixels or percentage, that overrides the original width of the image, causing the image to be scaled to the new width.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hjb1665703107869.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hjb1665703107869.html\" title=\"Widget property that specifies the height of the displayed image in a static server page as a number of pixels, or as a percentage of the original image height. This property sets the height attribute of an &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout and the image is scaled to fit.\">Height (u_height)</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__2\">\n Height, in pixels or percentage, that overrides the original height of the image, causing the image to be scaled to the new height.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pne1665703108090.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pne1665703108090.html\" title=\"In a static server page, exclude the field or entity if it does not need to be sent to the browser.\">Exclude</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xrv1665703127316__table_d14147e1_d14148e1_d14149e1__entry__2\">\n Do not load the field into the server page; use only if the field does not need to be sent to the browser.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xrv1665703127316__topic_d81757e1_d81758e1_d81759e1_d81760e1_d81761e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d371695e354\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xrv1665703127316__p_d115223e1_d115224e1_d115225e1\">When the field definition is copied to the layout, the XHTML source code similar to the following:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;x-subst name=\"IMAGE.MY_ENTITY.MY_MODEL\" type=\"image\"&gt;\n &lt;a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\"&gt;\n &lt;img name=\"IMAGE.MY_ENTITY.MY_MODEL\"\n src=\"file:///D:/Uniface/project/p1.jpg\" lowsrc=\"\"\n alt=\"\" border=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\"&gt;\n &lt;/a&gt;\n&lt;/x-subst&gt;\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rpw1719469985019.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Picture</a><p>This widget displays an image located in a directory defined at runtime, based on assignment settings.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7424959\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7424959\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Image Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 27, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Image This widget displays an image that can represent a hyperlink, have alternative text, or make use of other features that are not available in the picture control. XHTML Specification: <x-subst type=\"image\"> For more information, see <x-subst type=\"WidgetType\"> . Widget Properties Table 1. Widget Properties Property Description/More Information Image Source (u_src) Path and file name of the image to display. Link Value (u_url) Target URL for a link. Target Window (u_target) Type of target window into which the linked page is loaded. Shadow Image (u_lowsrc) Path and file name of a low-resolution image to display in the server page while the main image is loading. Alternative Text (u_alt) Text that is displayed if the image cannot be loaded. Alignment (u_align) Determines how the image is aligned in the field. Border (u_border) Width, in pixels, of the border that surrounds the image. Horizontal Spaces (u_hspace) Number of pixels of white space to be inserted to the left and right of the image. Vertical Spaces (u_vspace) Number of pixels of white space to be inserted above and below the image. Width (u_width) Width, in pixels or percentage, that overrides the original width of the image, causing the image to be scaled to the new width. Height (u_height) Height, in pixels or percentage, that overrides the original height of the image, causing the image to be scaled to the new height. Exclude Do not load the field into the server page; use only if the field does not need to be sent to the browser. Description When the field definition is copied to the layout, the XHTML source code similar to the following: <x-subst name=\"IMAGE.MY_ENTITY.MY_MODEL\" type=\"image\"> <a href=\"\" target=\"_blank\"> <img name=\"IMAGE.MY_ENTITY.MY_MODEL\" src=\"file:///D:/Uniface/project/p1.jpg\" lowsrc=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\"> </a> </x-subst> Copy Related Links Picture This widget displays an image located in a directory defined at runtime, based on assignment settings. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}